29/*
30 * Simple open hash tab implementation.
31 *
32 * Authors:
33 * Thomas Hellstr√∂m <thomas-at-tungstengraphics-dot-com>
34 */
35
36#ifndef DRM_HASHTAB_H
37#define DRM_HASHTAB_H
38
39#define drm_hash_entry(_ptr, _type, _member) container_of(_ptr, _type, _member)
40
41struct drm_hash_item {
42 LIST_ENTRY(drm_hash_item) head;
43 unsigned long key;
44};
45
46struct drm_open_hash {
47 LIST_HEAD(drm_hash_item_list, drm_hash_item) *table;
48 unsigned int size;
49 unsigned int order;
50 unsigned long mask;
51};
52
53extern int drm_ht_create(struct drm_open_hash *ht, unsigned int order);
54extern int drm_ht_insert_item(struct drm_open_hash *ht, struct drm_hash_item *item);
55extern int drm_ht_just_insert_please(struct drm_open_hash *ht, struct drm_hash_item *item,
56 unsigned long seed, int bits, int shift,
57 unsigned long add);
58extern int drm_ht_find_item(struct drm_open_hash *ht, unsigned long key, struct drm_hash_item **item);
59
60extern void drm_ht_verbose_list(struct drm_open_hash *ht, unsigned long key);
61extern int drm_ht_remove_key(struct drm_open_hash *ht, unsigned long key);
62extern int drm_ht_remove_item(struct drm_open_hash *ht, struct drm_hash_item *item);
63extern void drm_ht_remove(struct drm_open_hash *ht);
64
65#endif
